articles.title: Rebel Wilson Names Sasha Baron Cohen as Star “Trying to Threaten Me” Over Her Memoir - Variety
articles.description: Rebel Wilson has revealed on social media that Sasha Baron Cohen is the star who has been sending her threats to stop her from publishing her memoir.
articles.content:
